ah be pleased with him, would ask Al-'Abbas ibn Abdul Muttalib to supplicate for Allah to send rain. Umar would say, \u201cO Allah, we used to ask our Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, to supplicate\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":36200,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/05\/16\/istisqa-raising-hands-dua\/","url_meta":{"origin":25489,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Istisqa: Raising hands to supplicate for rain","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 16, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, would not raise his hands for any supplication except to pray for rain. He would raise them until we saw the skin of his armpits. Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 3565, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 895 Grade: Muttafaqun Alayhi (authenticity agreed upon)\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":36193,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/05\/16\/salat-al-istisqa\/","url_meta":{"origin":25489,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Istisqa: The Prophet prays and supplicates for rain","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 16, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Zayd reported: I saw the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, one day go out to prayer for rain. He turned his back to the people and faced the Qiblah and supplicated, then he turns his cloak insi